name: Lion heART
description:
Original one of a kind hand painted with acrylic paint.

Hi, I’m Ann-Marie Cheung, Visionary Artist and Creative Experience Guide.

I help adventurous spirits create a joyful, magical space in their lives with my unique, vibrant, whimsical artwork. I invite you into my fascinating world of exotic colours, ancient patterns, ornate textures and rich symbolism where I am constantly exploring and creating with acrylics, mixed media and digital tools.
